{"tid":2191781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"希望主流媒體對勇武手足公平少少","createTime":"2020-09-06T16:03:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-07T05:22:26.000Z","uid":72602,"like":120,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"61432682b936fd941e394b2174e68691bad9e642","tid":2191781,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:03:09.000Z","msg":"個細路女比狗搞係慘 但最尾啲狗都要放<br />\n主流媒體用幾個post去引迴響都無問題<br />\n但反而比便衣狗打拖地磨面嘅手足<br />\n大家留意下 呢單係一個篇幅都無 <br />\n得啲網絡小媒報導 抗爭page見到<br />\n人地無拿拿見比無證便衣狗打 點知咩事<br />\n以為721啲黑社會趁機搞事打手足<br />\n想幫/救人果幾位仲比啲狗粗暴對待<br />\n噴勁扯褲磨地流哂血拖左成條街受傷<br />\n唔洗放到媒大 出番一篇報導等更多人知<br />\n見到啲便衣狗濫暴 報道番出黎<br />\n佢地要受48 唔知幾多條罪 提堂<br />\n非批鬥 希望主流媒體對佢地公平少少"},{"pid":"b03819e7bf64d7c619d0c9c4e22fd3fdd36a650e","tid":2191781,"uid":72602,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:03:37.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以幫手推<br />\n呢件事都絕對值得上新聞"},{"pid":"4d5ccfa9098d92faefadf7b0963eff17fea3348d","tid":2191781,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:04:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"38d3ba823deac0c80174c2032afedcca9813847b","tid":2191781,"uid":59976,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:05:31.000Z","msg":"人地睇邊樣畫面最靚就報邊個先架啦，唔係點吸引人睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93bf9ab62ae3a83dd5bff43dd87a903c2c842230","tid":2191781,"uid":21028,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:05:58.000Z","msg":"我只同意有鎗果邊嘅武力關注度要極高 <br />\n屌 你有炮 唔影你唔通影條友打飛機先啱 <br />\n傳媒緊係要睇住班隨時走火殺人"},{"pid":"4f9007d80bd3053e33d9cf02fef987715ba5ae72","tid":2191781,"uid":72602,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T16:06:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1178706375559427/posts/3336789593084417/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1178706375559427%2Fposts%2F3336789593084417%2F&d=uo2GI0poDlFkSsUZ5iwE4kYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=45a5adbd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.faceb